hadiths[106]{hadithnumber,text}:
7024,"hamein Zuhair bin Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abu-Ishaq ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein nikley, usmein logon ko bahut takleef pahunchi to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne apne sathiyon se kaha : jo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hain, jab tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se alag na ho jayen, un par kuchh kharch na karo (muhajireen se taawun band kar do) Zuhair ne kaha : aur ye uski qirat hai jisne ( Haula ( ko zer ke sath min ( Haula ( padha aur us ne (ye bhi) kaha : agar ham Madina ko lot gaey to jo izzat waley hain wo wahan se zillat walon ko nikal dengey. ( Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua aur aapko ye baat bata di, aap ne Abdullah-bin Ubai ko bulwaya aur us se (is baat ke mutaalliq) poochha, us ne bahut pakki qism khaai ke usne aisa nahi kaha aur kaha : Zaid ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jhoot bola hai. (Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : mere dil ko un logon ki is baat se bahut takleef pahunchi, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne meri tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil ki : jab aap ke paas munaafeqeen aatey hain phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke istighfar ke liye unko bulwaya to unhon-ne (tamaskhur se) apne sar tedhey kar liye aur (is aayat mein) Allah Taala ke qaul : maano wo sahaarey se khadey huey shehteer hain (se murad (Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (ye hai ke) ye log ( jismani eitibaar se seedhey , lambey aur dekhney mein) bahut khoobsurat they."
7025,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr (bin Dinar) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye bayan kartey huey suna : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abdullah-bin-Ubai ki qabr par tashrif laaey, usko qabr se nikal kar apne ghutnon par rakha, is par apna luaab Mubarak chhidka aur usey apni qamees pahnaai, (aisa kyon kiya?) Allah zyada jaanney wala hai."
7026,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne khabar di, kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abdullah-bin-Ubai ke paas usko iske gadhey mein dakhil kar diye janey ke baad aaey, phir Sufiyan ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
7027,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool mar gaya to iske betey Abdullah bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey, aur aap se sawal kya ke aap apni qamees usko ata farmaein , jis mein wo apne bap ko kafan dein to aap ne (wo qamees ( unko ata ki, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke aap uski namaaze-janaaza padhein , chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par namaaze-janaaza padhney ke liye khadey huey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho gaey aur (iltija karne ke liye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey (ke aik kinarey) ko pakad liya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya aap uski namaaze-janaaza padhaaengey, halanke Allah Taala ne aapko uski namaaze-janaaza padhney se mana farmaya hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujhey ikhtiyar diya hai, us ne farmaya hai : aap unke liye istighfar karein ya istighfar na karein, chahe aap unke liye 70 martaba istighfar karein aur main 70 martaba se zyada istighfar karunga. (Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : yaqinan wo munafiq hai, (magar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski namaaze-janaaza padha di, is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (waazeh hukm) nazil farmaya : aur un (munaafeqeen) mein se jo shakhs mar jaey aap kabhi uski namaaze-janaaza na padhein aur na uski qabr par khadey hon."
7028,Yahya qattaan ne Ubaidullah (bin-Umar-bin-Hafs ( se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki aur mazeed ye kaha : chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un par namaaze-janaaza tark kar di.
7029,"Muhammad-bin-abi-Umar Makki ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne abu-Ma'mar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : teen aadmi Baitullah ke paas ikatthey huey, ( unmein se) do qureshi they aur aik Saqafi tha, ya do Saqafi they aur aik qureshi tha, unke dilon ka faham (samajh) kam tha, unke peton ki charbi bahut thi. unmein se aik ne kaha : kya tum samajhtey ho ke jo kuchh ham kehtey hain, Allah sunta hai? doosrey ne kaha : agar ham unchi awaz se baat karein to sunta hai aur aahista baat karein to nahi sunta. teesrey ne kaha : agar ham uncha bolein to wo sunta hai,  phir ham aahista bolein to bhi sunta hai. is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye aayatein ( nazil farmaein : tum isliye (apni baatein ( nahi chipa rahe they ke tumharey khilaf tumharey kaan gawahi dengey aur na tumhari aankhen aur na tumhari khaalein ."
7030,"Abu-Bakar-bin-khallaad baahili ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Sulaiman ne Umara-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Wahab-bin-Rabee se aur unhon-ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi ke saath hamein Yahya ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Mansoor ne Mujahid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Ma'mar se aur unhon-ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat ki."
7031,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Adi-bin-Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Yazeed ko Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jang ke liye) uhud ki taraf rawaana huey. jo log aap ke sath they unmein se kuchh wapas aa gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba unke barey mein do hisson mein taqseem ho gaey. kuchh ne kaha : ham unhein qatl kar dein aur kuchh ne kaha : nahi. to (ye aayat) nazil hui : tumhen kya ho gaya hai ke munaafeqeen ke barey main tum do giroh ban gaey ho."
7032,Yahya-bin-Saeed aur ghandar donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7033,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein kuchh munaafeqeen aisey they ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi jang ke liye tashrif ley jatey to wo peechhey reh jatey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mukhalifat mein apne peechhey reh janey par khush hotey, aur jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas aatey to aap ke samney uzr bayan kartey aur qasmein khaatey aur chahtey ke log un kaamon par unki tareef karein jo unhon-ne nahi kiye they. is par ye ( aayat nazil ( hui : ''un logon ke mutaalliq guman na karo jo apne kiye par khush hotey hain aur ye pasand kartey hain ke us kaam par unki tareef ki jaey jo unhon-ne nahi kiya, unke mutaalliq ye guman bhi na karo ke wo azab se bchney waley maqam par hongey.''"
7034,"ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ibne-abi-Mulaika ne bataya, unhein Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne khabar di ke Marwan ne apne darban se kaha : Raafe! Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jao aur kaho ke agar ye baat hai ke ham mein se har shakhs jo apne kiye par khush hota hai aur har aik jo ye pasand karta hai ke jo usney nahi kya, is par uski tareef ki jaey, usko azab hoga to ham sab hi zaroor azab mein daley jaengey. to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum logon ka is aayat se kya talluq (banta) hai? ye aayat ahle-kitab ke barey mein utri thi, phir Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne (is se pehle) ye aayat padhi : aur jab Allah ne un logon ka, jinhein kitab di gaee thi, ahad liya ke tum usey logon ke samney khol kar bayan karogey aur usko chhipaaogey nahi. phir Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne (uske baad wali) aayat tilawat farmai : un logon ke barey mein guman na karo jo apne kiye par khush hotey hain aur pasand kartey hain ke is kaam par unki tareef ki jaey jo unhon-ne nahi kya aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse (unki kitab mein likhi hui) kisi cheez ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne aap se wo cheez chipa li aur (iske bajaey) aik dusri baat bata di aur wo is tarah nikley ke unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ye zahir kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse jo puchha tha, unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wahi bata diya hai aur is baat par unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tareef bhi batorni chahi aur jo baat aap ne unse poochhi wo baat chipa kar unhon-ne jo kuchh liya tha is par (apne dilon mein) khush bhi huey."
7035,"Aswad bin Aamir ne kaha : hamein Shoba bin Hajjaj ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Qais (bin Ibad ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap ne apne us kaam par ghaur kya jo aap ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley mein kya hai) unka bharpur sath diya hai aur unke mukhalifon se jang tak ki hai) ye aap ke apne ghaur-fikr se ikhtiyar ki hui aap ki raey thi ya aisi cheez thi jiski zimme-dari Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aap logon ke sipurd ki thi? unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi aisi zimme-dari hamarey sipurd nahi ki jo unhon-ne tamam logon ke sipurd na ki ho lekin Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere sathiyon mein se baara afraad munafiq hain, unmein se aath (8) aisey hain jo jannat mein dakhil nahi hongey yahan tak ke oont soi ke naakey mein dakhil ho jaey ( kabhi dakhil nahi hongey), unmein aath (8) aisey hain (ke unke shar se nijat ke liye unke kandhon ke darmyan zahir honey wala surkh) phoda tumhari nijat ke liye tumhen kifaayat karega aur char .) aagey ka hissa ( mujhey ( Aswad bin Aamir ko) yad nahi ke Shoba ne un ( char (ke barey mein kya kaha tha."
7036,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ghandar ( ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Qais-bin Ibad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham logon ne Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki himaayat mein) apni jang ko kaisey dekhtey hain, kya ye aik raey hai jo aap ne ghaur-fikr se ikhtiyar ki hai? to raey ghalat bhi ho sakti hai aur sahi bhi, ya koi zimme-dari hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum logon ke sipurd ki thi? to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein koi aisi (khususi) zimme-dari nahi di thi jo tamam logon ke sipurd na ki ho aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : be-shak meri ummat mein. padhi. Shoba ne kaha : aur main samajhta hun ke unhon-ne kaha tha : mujhey Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ye) hadis sunai aur ghandar ne kaha : mujhey lagta hai ke unhon-ne kaha : meri ummat mein baara munafiq hain, wo jannat mein dakhil na hongey aur na uski khushbu paeingey, jab tak ke oont soi ke naakey mein dakhil na ho jaey. unmein se aath (8) aisey hain (ke unke shar se bachao ke liye) tumhari kifaayat aik aisa phodaa karega jo aag ke jaltey huey dene ki tarah (uper se surkh) hoga, unke kandhon mein zahir hoga yahan tak ke unke seenon se nikal aayega."
7037,"Waleed bin Jame ne kaha : hamein abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Aqba walon mein se aik shakhs aur Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan (is tarah ka ( jhagda ho gaya jis tarah logon ke darmyan ho jata hai. (guftgu ke doran mein) unhon-ne (is shakhs se) kaha : main tumhen Allah ki qism de kar poochhta hun ke Aqba walon ki tadaad kitni thi? (hazrat abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : logon ne us se kaha : jab wo aap se poochh rahe hain to unhein bataao. (phir Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne khud hi jawab detey huey) kaha : hamein bataya jata tha ke wo chaudah log they aur agar tum bhi unmein shamil they, to wo kal pandarah log they aur main gawahi deta hun ke unmein se baara duniya ki zindagi mein bhi Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khilaf jang mein they aur (aakhirat mein bhi) jab gawah khadey hongey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un teen logon ka uzr qabool farma liya tha jinhoney kaha tha ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke elaan karne waley ka elaan nahi suna tha aur is baat se bhi be khabar they ke un logon ka irada kya hai jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Harra mein they, aap chal padey aur farmaya : pani kam hai, isliye mujh se pahley wahan koi na pahunchey. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( wahan pahunch kar) dekha ke kuchh log aap se pahley wahan pahunch gaey hain to aap ne us roz un par laanat ki."
7038,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Qurra bin Khalid ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kon hai jo us ghaati (yani) muraar ki ghaati par chadhega! be-shak iske gunah bhi isi tarah jhad jaeinge jis tarah Bani-Israeel ke gunah jhad gaey they. (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to sabse pahley jo us ghaati par chadhey wo hamarey banu-khazraj ke ghody they, phir logon ka taanta bandh gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum sab wo ho jinke gunah bakhsh diye gaey, siwaey surkh oont waley shakhs ke. ham uske paas aaey aur (is se) kaha : aao Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumharey liye bhi istighfar farmaein. usne kaha : Allah ki qasam! agar main apni gum shuda cheez paalun to ye baat mujhey uski nisbat zyada pasand hai ke tumhara sahib mere liye maghfirat ki dua kare. (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : wo aadmi us waqt apni kisi gum shuda cheez ko dhoondney ke liye aawaazein laga raha tha."
7039,"Yahya bin Habib Haarisi ne hamein yahi hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Khalid-bin Haris ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Qurra ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kon hai jo muraar ya muraar ki ghaati par chadhega. (aagey) Muaz Anbari ki hadis ki tarah, albatta (is hadis mein) unhon-ne kaha : aur wo aik dehati tha jo apni gum shuda cheez dhoondney ke liye elaan karne ke liye aaya tha."
7040,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : ham mein banu-Najjaar mein se aik shakhs tha, us ne sura-Baqara aur sura-aale-Imran padhi (yaad ki) hui thi aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kitabat kiya karta tha, wo bhag kar chala gaya aur ahle-kitab ke sath shamil ho gaya, unhon-ne usko bahut uncha uthaya aur kaha : ye hai jo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kitabat karta tha wo uske aaney se bahut khush huey, thodey hi din guzrey ke Allah Taala ne unke beech mein (hotey huey) uski gardan tod di. unhon-ne uske liye qabr khodi aur usey dafn kar diya. subah hui to zamin ne usey apni satah ke uper phenk diya tha. unhon-ne dobara wahi kiya, uski qabr khodi aur usey dafn kar diya. phir subah hui to zamin ne usey bahar phenk diya tha, unhon-ne phir (teesri baar) isi tarah kiya, uske liye qabr khodi aur usey dafn kar diya, subah ko zamin ne usey bahar phenk diya.to unhon-ne usey isi tarah phainkaa hua chhod diya."
7041,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar se waapas aaey, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina Munawra ke qareeb they, to itney zor ki aandhi chali ke qareeb tha wo sawar ko bhi (ret mein) dafn kar degi. to wo (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) yaqin se kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ye aandhi kisi munafiq ki maut ke liye bheji gaee hai jab aap Madina Munawra tashrif ley aaey to munaafiqon mein se aik bahut bada munafiq mar chuka tha."
7042,"Ayas (bin-Salma-bin-Akwa) ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik shakhs ki, jisey bukhar chadhaa hua tha, iyaadat ki, kaha : maine us (ke jism ( par apna hath rakha to maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine aaj ki tarah kisi shakhs ko nahi dekha jo us se zyada tap raha ho. to Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen qiyamat ke din us se bhi zyada taptey hue ke barey mein na bataaun? ye donon shakhs jo (oonton par) sawar hain, apne munh dusri taraf kiye huey hain. (aap ne ye baat ( do aadmiyon ke barey mein) farmai ( jo us waqt ( zahir taur (aap ke sathiyon mein) shumaar hotey ( they."
7043,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : munafiq ki misal us bakri ki tarah hai jo bakriyon ke do rewadon ke darmyan mimiyaati hui bhaagii phirti hai kabhi bhag kar is rewad mein jati hai aur kabhi us taraf jati hai. ( kisi bhi aik rewad ka hissa nahi hoti.)"
7044,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : palat kar aik baar is ( rewad ( mein aati hai aur dusri baar usmein."
7045,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din aik bahut bada (aur ( mota aadmi aayega, (lekin)  Allah Taala ke nazdeek wo ( wazan mein) machchar ke par ke barabar bhi na hoga (ye aayat ( padh lo : ''to ham qiyamat ke din unke liye koi wazan qaaim nahi karengey.''"
7046,"Fuzail-bin-ayaaz ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Ubeda salmaani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik Yahudi aalim Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ya kaha : abul-Qaasim ! be-shak Allah Taala qiyamat ke din aasmanon ko aik ungli par rakh lega, aur zaminon ko aik ungli par, aur pahadon aur darakhton ko aik ungli par aur pani aur geeli mitti ko aik ungli par aur tamam makhlooq ko aik ungli par thaam lega.  phir unko bulaeyga aur farmaeyga : badshah main hun, badshah main hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us Yahudi aalim ki baat par tajjub aur uske tasdeeq kartey huey hansey, phir aap ne (ye aayat ( padhi : ''unhon-ne is tarah Allah ki qadr nahi ki jis tarah uski qadr karne ka haq hai. saari zamin aur sab ke sab aasman qiyamat ke din i\uske daain hath mein liptey huey hongey. wo (har us cheez ki sharaakat se) paak aur buland hai jinhein wo (uske saath) Sharik kartey hain."
7047,"Jarir ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, kaha : yahood mein se aik aalim Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, Fuzel ki hadis ki tarah , aur is mein ye bayan nahi kiya : wo ( Allah ( un ( ungliyon ( ko hilaaey ga aur) Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap is baat par tajjub se uski tasdeeq kartey huey (is tarah) hansey ke aap ke pichhley dandaan Mubarak zahir ho gaey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne (is tarah) Allah ki qadr nahi ki (jis tarah) uski qadr karne ka haq hai. (aur ( poori ( aayat tilawat farmai."
7048,"Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Ibrahim ko kehtey huey suna : maine Alqama ko kehtey huey suna ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ahle-kitab mein se aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur us ne kaha : abul-Qaasim ! be-shak Allah Taala tamam aasmanon ko aik ungli par, zaminon ko aik ungli par aur darakhton aur geeli mitti ko aik ungli par aur tamam makhlooq ko aik ungli par thaam lega. phir farmaeyga : badshah main hun, badshah main hun. ( ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap (is baat par) hans padey yahan tak ke aap ke pichhley dandaane-mubarak zahir huey, phir aap ne (is aayat ki) tilawat ki : unhon-ne Allah Taala ki (is tarah) qadr nahi pahchaani jis tarah qadr pahchaanney ka haq hai."
7049,"abu-Muawiya, Esa-bin-Yonus aur Jarir sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, magar un sab ki riwayaton mein hai : aur darakhton ko aik ungli par aur geeli mitti ko aik ungli par thaam lega aur Jarir ki hadis mein ye nahi hai aur makhlooq ko aik ungli par thaamey ga lekin uski hadis mein ye hai : aur pahadon ko aik ungli par thaam lega aur unhon-ne Jarir ki hadis mein mazeed ye kaha : uski baat ki tasdeeq aur is par tajjub ka izhar kartey huey (aap hansey)."
7050,"ibne-Musaiyab ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kiya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala qiyamat ke din zamin ko apni muththi mein ley lega aur aasman ko apne daahiney hath mein lapet lega , phir farmaeyga : badshah main hun, zamin ke badshah kahan hain?"
7051,"Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah qiyamat ke din aasmanon ko lapetey ga , phir unko daain hath se pakad lega aur farmaeyga : badshah main hun. ( aaj dusron par) jabr karne waley kahan hain? takabbur karne waley kahan hain? phir baain hath se zamin ko lapet lega , phir farmaeyga : badshah main hun, (aaj) jabr karne waley kahan hain? takabbur karne waley kahan hain?"
7052,"Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : mujhey abu-Hazim ne Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf dekha ke wo (hadis bayan kartey huey amalan) kis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah karke dikhaatey hain. (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah apne aasmanon aur apni zaminon ko apne donon hathon se pakad lega phir farmaeyga main Allah, main badshah hun aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ungliyon ko band kartey they aur kholtey they. yahan tak ke maine member ko dekha, wo apne nichley hissey se (lekar ooper ke hissey tak) hil raha tha. yahan tak ke maine kaha : kya wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar gir jaeyga?"
7053,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Hazim ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par dekha jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : ( Allah ( jabbaar aasmanon aur apni zaminon ko apne hathon mein pakad lega . phir Yaqoob ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7054,"Suraij-bin-Yoonus aur Harun-bin-Abdullah ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Hujjaj-bin-Muhammad ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Ismail-bin-Umayya ne Ayub-bin-Khalid se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah-bin-Raafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera hath pakda, phir farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne mitti ( zamin ( ko haftey ke din paida kiya aur is mein pahadon ko itwaar ke din paida kiya aur darakhton ko pair ke din paida kiya aur na-pasandida chizon ko mangal ke din paida kiya aur noor ko buddh ke din paida kiya aur is mein chaupaayon ko jumerat ke din phaila diya aur sab makhlooqat ke aakhir mein Adam (Alaihissalam) ko Juma ke din Asr ke baad se lekar raat tak ke darmyan Juma (ke din ke aakhiri ghanto mein se kisi ghadi mein paida farmaya. juloodi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Imam Muslim rahmatulla ke shagird Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Husain-bin-Ali bistaami, Sahal-bin-Ammar, Hafs ke nawaasey Ibrahim aur dusron ne Hajjaj se yahi hadis bayan ki."
7055,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din logon ko ghubaar ki rangat mili , safaid zamin par ikattha kiya jaeyga, jaisey chhaney huey aatey ki roti hoti hai aur us zamin mein kisi shakhs ke liye koi alamat maujood nahi hogi."
7056,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke us qaul ke mutaalliq sawal kiya : jis din zamin dusri zamin se badal di jaeygi aur aasman ( bhi badal diya jaaeyga) to Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! us din log kahan hongey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pul) raaste par.
7057,ataa-bin-Yasar ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din ye zamin aik hi roti bin jaeygi. jabbaar ( Allah Taala ( ahle-jannat ki mehmani ke liye usey apne hath se ulat palat kar roti ki tarah bana dega jis tarah tum mein se koi shakhs safar mein roti ko ulat palat karta hai. (Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : itney mein yahudiyon mein se aik shakhs aa gaya usne kaha : abul-Qaasim Rehman aap par barkat nazil farmaai ! kya main aapko qiyamat ke roz ahle-jannat ki ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) ke barey mein na bataaun? aap ne irshad farmaya : kyon nahi ! ( bataao ( usne kaha : zamin aik ( badi si ( roti bin jaeygi. jis tarah ( uski aamad se qabl khud ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha. (abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari taraf dekha phir aap hansey yahan tak ke aap ke pichhley dandaane-mubarak nazar aaney lagey. us ne ( phir ( kaha : kya main aapko unke saalan ke barey mein na bataaun? aap ne farmaya : kyon nahi (bataao \) usne kaha unka saalan bil-aam aur noon hoga. sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne puchha wo kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bail aur machhli . iske jigar ke chhotey se izaafi hissey ko (juwa asl jigar ke sath aik taraf maujood hota hai) sattar (70) hazaar log khaaengey.
7058,Muhammad-bin-Sirin ne hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar das (10) (badey) Yahudi (aalim) meri pairwi kar letey to poori zamin par koi Yahudi baqi na rehta magar musalman ho jata.
7059,"Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim ne Alqama se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik martaba main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik khet mein chala ja raha tha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ki aik shaakh ka sahara ley  (kar chal) rahe they ke aap ka yahood ke chand logon ke qareeb se guzar hua unmein se aik ne doosrey se kaha : unse Rooh ke barey mein sawal karo phir wo aik doosrey se kehney lagey : unke barey main tumhen shak kis baat ka hai? aisa na ho ke wo aagey se aisi baat keh dein jo tumhen buri lagey phir unmein se aik shakhs khada ho kar aap ke paas aa gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Rooh ke barey mein sawal kiya. (hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( thodi der ke liye) khamosh ho gaey aur unko koi jawab na diya. mujhey malum ho gaya ke aap par wahi nazil ho rahi hai, kaha: main bhi apni jagah par (ruk kar) khada ho gaya. jab wahi nazil ho chuki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye padhtey huey) farmaya : ''ye log aap se Rooh ke barey mein sawal kartey hain. keh dijiye Rooh mere rab ke hukm se hai aur tum (insanon) ko bahut kam ilm diya gaya hai.''"
7060,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu ash'ajj ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki, isi ke saath hamein Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim Hanzali aur Ali-bin-khashram ne bhi hadis bayan ki donon ne kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di. un donon (Wakee aur Esa) ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke aik (ujdey huey) khet mein ja raha tha. Hafs ki hadis ki tarah , magar Wakee ki hadis mein hai :                                                 ( وَمَا أُوتِيتُم مِّنَ الْعِلْمِ إِلَّا قَلِيلًا )                                                                                                                                                          ''aur tum logon ko ilm ka thoda hissey hi diya gaya hai.''                                                                                                        (jis tarah Quran ki mash-hoor mutwaatir qirat hai. aur Esa-bin-Yonus ki is riwayat mein jo unse ( Ali ( bin-khashram ne bayan ki hai) وما اوتوا ( unhein nahi diya gaya ke alfaz hain."
7061,"abu-Saeed ash'ajj ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Idris se suna wo keh rahe they, maine Aamash se suna wo is riwayat ko Abdullah-bin-Murra se aur wo Masruq se aur wo Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ke darakhton mein (khajoor ki) aik shaakh ka sahara liye huey (chaley ja rahe) they phir Aamash se un sab ki hadis ke mutabiq bayan kiya aur unhon-ne (bhi) apni riwayat mein mashhoor aur mutwaatir qirat ke mutabiq ( وَمَا أُوتِيتُم مِّنَ الْعِلْمِ إِلَّا قَلِيلًا ( bayan kiya. un riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hars (khet) aur nakhl (khajoor ke darakhton) ke darmyan ja rahe they. sahi Bukhari ki aik riwayat mein hars hai. (hadis 4721) jabke dusri riwayat mein kharab (ujaad jagah) hai. (hadis : 125 (us se malum hota hai ke wo khet jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaley ja rahe they. Madina ke aam kheton ki tarah khajoor ke baagh mein tha aur ab usmein kuchh kaasht nahi ho raha tha ujdaa hua aur naahamwaar honey ki wjah se aap uske andar khujoor ki shaakh ka sahara lekar chal rahe they. jaame-Tirmizi mein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rooh ke mutaalliq yahudiyon se poochh kar Quraish Makka ne bhi sawal kiya tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko bhi yahi jawab diya tha (jaame-Tirmizi hadis 3140 ( Madina mein jab yahood ne khud sawal kiya to chunkey wo ahle-kitab they isliye ye imkan tha ke unki kitab mein yahi baat kisi aur rang mein kahi gaee ho aur wo andaz ke us ikhtilaf ko apne liye daleel banaaney ki koshish karein isliye jawab deney se pahley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne twaqquf kiya (thehrey) aur Allah Taala ne dobara wahi jawab 'wahi' farma diya jo Taurait ke theek mutabiq tha aur yahood ko apne liye aap ki risalat se inkar ka koi uzr na mil saka."
7062,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu zuhaa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Khabbaab (bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha mera kuchh qarz Aas-bin-Waail ke zimmey tha. main us se qarz ka taqaza karne ke liye uske paas gaya to usne mujh se kaha : main us waqt tak tumhen adaaeygi nahi karunga, yahan tak ke tum naauzubillah Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kufr karo. kaha : maine us se kaha : tum mar kar dobara zinda ho jaogey , phir bhi mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kufr nahi karunga. usne kaha : aur main maut ke baad dobara zinda kiya jaaunga? to (us waqt) jab main dobara maal aur aulad ke paas pahunch jaaunga to tumhen adaaeygi kar doonga. Wakee ne kaha : Aamash ne isi tarah kaha : unhon-ne kaha : is par ye aayat nazil hui : ''kya aap ne us shakhs ko dekha jisne hamari aayaton se kufr kiya'' aur kaha : mujhey (apna) maal aur (apni) aulad zaroori di jaeygi se lekar us (Allah  ke farman aur wo hamarey paas akelaa aayega, tak."
7063,abu-Muawiya Abdullah-bin-Numair Jarir aur Sufiyan sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath Wakee ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur Jarir ki hadis mein hai. (Hazrat Khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main zamana jahiliyat mein lohaar tha to maine Aas-bin-Waail ke liye kaam kiya phir main us se ( ujrat ka ( taqaza karne ke liye aaya.
7064,Shoba ne abdul-Hameed-zyadi se riwayat ki unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : wo keh rahe they ke abu-jahal ne kaha : aey Allah ! agar (ye jo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lekar aaey hain) yahi teri taraf se haq hai to ham par aasman se patthar barsa de ya ham par koi dardnak azab ley aa . to is par (aayat) nazil hui : ''Allah taala us waqt un par (is tarah ka ( azab bhejney wala na tha jabke aap bhi unmein maujood they aur Allah Taala unko azab dene wala na tha jab wo (alehadgi mein) istighfar kiye ja rahe they aur unhein kya hai ke Allah unhein azab na de jabke wo (iman laney walon ko) Masjide-Haram se roktey hain.'' aayat ke aakhir tak.
7065,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz aur Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala Qaisi ne hamein hadis bayan ki donon ne kaha : hamein Moatamir ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Nuaim-bin-abi-Hind ne abu-Hazim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : abu-Jahal ne kaha : kya Muhammad tum logon ke samney apna chehra zamin par rakhtey hain? (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to kaha gaya : haan. chunanche usne kaha : laat aur uzzaa ki qism ! agar maine unko aisa kartey huey dekh liya to main unki gardan ko raundon ga ya unke chehrey ko mitti mein milaaun ga (Naauzubillah ! ( kaha : phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh rahe they wo aap ke paas aaya aur ye irada kiya ke aap ki gardan Mubarak ko raundey ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to wo unhein achcha eidiyon ke bal palat'taa hua aur apne donon hathon (ko aagey karke un ( se apna bachao karta hua nazar aaya. ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to us se kaha kya : tumhen kya hua? to usne kaha : mere aur uske darmyan aag ki aik khandaq aur sakht hol ( paida karne wali makhlooq (aur bahut se par they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo mere qareeb aata to Farishtey uske eik-eik uzu (khaas ang) ko uchak letey. (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : is par Allah Taala ne ye aayatein nazil farmaein. (abu-Hazim ne kaha) hamein malum nahi ke ye Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hui ( apni hadis hai ya unhein (kisi ki taraf se) pahunchi hai. (wo aayatein ye thin) iske siwa koi baat nahi ke insan har sura mein sarkashi karta hai. is liye ke wo khud ko dekhta hai ke wo har aik se mustaghni (be-niyazi) hai. haqiqat ye hai ke) usey (aap ke rab ki taraf wapas jana hai. aap ne usey dekha jo roktaa hai. ( Allah ke) bandey ko jab wo Namaz ada karta hai. kya tum ne dekha ke agar wo ( Allah ka banda ( hidayat par ho aur taqwe ka hukm deta ho (to rokney waley ka kya banega ?) kya aap ne dekha ke aa kar us yani abu jahal ne jhutlaayaa hai aur hidayat se munh phera hai. (to) kya wo nahi janta ke Allah dekhta hai. hargiz nahi ! agar wo baaz na aaya to ham (usey) peshani se pakad kar kheenchein gey. (uski) jhooti gunah karne wali peshani se, phir wo apni majlis ko (madad ke liye) pukaarey, ham azab dene waley farishton ko bulaaengey. hargiz nahi ! aap uski (koi baat bhi) na maanein. Ubaidullah (bin-Muaz) ne apni hadis mein mazeed kaha, ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( أَوْ أَمَرَ بِالتَّقْوَىٰ ( ki tafseer kartey huey) kaha : aur is baat ka hukm deta ho jiska us ( Allah ( ne usey hukm diya hai. aur) Muhammad ( bin-Abdul-Aala ne mazeed ye kaha : wo apni majlis ko pukaarey yani apni qaum ko."
7066,"Mansoor ne abu zuha (Muslim-bin sabeeh) se, unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ke paas baithey huey they aur wo hamarey darmyan (apne bistar ya bichhoney par) letey huey they, to aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : abu Abdur-Rehman ! abwaab kanda (Kufa ka aik mahalla) mein aik qissa bhale hi ( waaiz ( aaya hua hai, wo waz (nasihat) kar raha hai aur ye kehta hai ke dhoein wali (Allah ki) nishani aaeygi aur (ye dhuan) kaafiron ki roohein qabz kar lega aur mominon ko ye zukam jaisi kaifiyat se do-char karega. Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha aur wo ghussey ke aalim mein uth kar baith gaey, logo! Allah se daro, tum mein se jo shakhs koi cheez janta ho, wo itni hi bayan karey jitni janta ho aur jo nahi janta, wo kahey : Allah zyada jaanney wala hai. be-shak wo (Allah taalaa) tum mein se usko (bhi) zyada jaanney wala hai. jo is baat ke barey mein jo wo nahi janta, ye kehta hai : Allah zyada jaanney wala hai. izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya : keh dijiye : main tum se koi ajr nahi mangta aur na hi banawat karne walon mein se hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab logon ki Deen se roo-gardaani dekhi to aap ne (dua kartey huey) farmaya : aey Allah ! (un par) Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke saat (7) saalon jaisey saat (7) saal ( bhej de. ( ) Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to unhein (qahat ke) aik saal ne aa liya jisne har cheez ka safaayaa kar diya, yahan tak ke un (mushrik) logon ne bhook se chamdey aur murdar tak khaaey. unmein se koi shakhs aasman ki taraf dekhta to usey dhoein ke jaisi aik cheez chhaai hui nazar aati . chunanche abu Sufiyan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap aaey hain, Allah ki itaat aur sila rehmi ka hukm detey hain, aap ki qaum (qahat aur bhook se) halaak ho rahi hai. unke liye Allah se dua karein. izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : aap us din ka intizar karein jab aasman aik nazar aaney waley dhoein ko ley aayega. (aur wo) logon ko dhanp lega. ye dardnak azab hoga, se lekar iske farman : be-shak tum (kufr mein) lot janey waley hogey tak. (hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : kya aakhirat ka azab hataya jaeyga ? jis din ham tum par badi giraft karengey (is din) ham intiqaam leney waley hongey. wo giraft badr ke din thi. ab tak dhoein ki nishani giraft aur chimat janey wala azab (badr mein shikast faash aur qatl) aur Rome (mojooda Itly) (ki fateh) ki nishani (sab ( aa kar guzar chuki hain."
7067,"abu-Muawiya , Wakee , aur Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim-bin Sabeeh se aur unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ke paas aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : main masjid mein aik aisey shakhs ko chhod kar aa raha hun jo apni raey se Quran Majeed ki tafseer karta hai wo ( Quran ki) aayat : jab aasman se waazeh dhuaan uthega ki tafseer karta hai, kehta hai : qiyamat ke din logon ke paas aik dhuaan aayega jo logon ki saanson ko giraft mein ley lega, yahan tak ke logon ko zukaam jaisi kaifiyat (jis mein saans leni mushkil ho jati hai) darpesh hogi, to Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : jiske paas ilm ho wo iske mutabiq baat kahey aur jo na janta ho, wo kahey : Allah zyada jaanney wala hai. ye baat insan ke faham (samajh) ( Deen (ka hissa hai. ke jis baat ko wo nahi janta uske barey mein kahey : Allah zyada jaanney wala hai. us (dhoein) ki haqiqat ye thi ke Quraish ne jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khilaf sakht nafarmani se kaam liya to aap ne unke khilaf Yusuf (Alaihissalam) (ke zamaney waale) qahat ke saalon jaisi qahat saali ki dua ki. unhein qahat aur tang dasti ne aa liya yahan tak ke) unmein se) koi shakhs aasman ki taraf dekhney lagta to bhook ki shiddat se usey apne aur aasman ke darmyan dhuan sa chhaya hua nazar aata yahan tak ke un logon ne (bhook ki shiddat se) haddiyaan tak khaain, chunanche (unmein se) aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap (qabeela) Muzar ke liye bakhshish talab farmaein. wo halaakat ka shikar hain, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Muzar ke liye? to bahut jurat wala hai (ke Allah se shirk aur uske rasool se bughz ke bawajud darkhaast kar raha hai ke main tumharey liye Allah se dua karun) kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( phir bhi) unke haq mein dua farma di. is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ( aayat ( nazil farmai : ham (tum se) thodey waqt ke liye azab hata detey hain. tum ( phir kufr hi mein) lotney waley ho. (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir un par barish barsaai gaee. unhein khush-haali mil gaee, kaha : (to phir ( wo apni usi ravish par lot gaey jis par pahley they. is par Allah Taala ne (ye hissa) nazil farmaya : aap intizar kijiye jab aasman zahir dhuaan ley aayega. jo logon ko dhanp lega, ye dardnak azab hoga. (phir ye aayat nazil farmai) jis din ham badi giraft mein lengey, ham intiqaam leney waley hongey. kaha : yani jange-badr ko."
7068,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu zuhaa se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : panch (nishaniyan) guzar chuki hain : dhuaan, chimat janey wala azab (badr ke din shikast aur halaakate) Rome (mojooda Itly) ki fateh (badr ke din 70 mushrikon ki giraftaari) sakht giraft aur chaand (ka 2 tukdey hona.)"
7069,Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7070,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne azra se unhon-ne Hasan Arni se, unhon-ne Yahyaa-bin-Jazaar se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke farman : aur badey azab se pahley ham unhein qareeb ka ( chhota ( azab chakhaaengey. (ki tafseer) ke barey mein riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha (usi) duniya mein pesh aaney waley masaaib, Rome (mojooda Itly) ki fateh, giraft (jange-badr) ya dhuaan (murad) hain. giraft aur dhoein ke barey mein shak karne waley Shoba hain. (unse uper ke rawiyon ne yaqin se bataya. Shoba ne kaha : unhein shak hua hai)"
7071,"Mujahid ne abu Mamar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahed mein chaand taqseem ho kar do tukdey ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( logo ! usko dekh lo aur) gawah bin jao."
7072,"abu-Muawiya, Hafs bin Ghiyas aur) Ali ( ibne-Mus-hir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim (Nakhai) se, unhon-ne abu Mamar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik baar ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina mein maujood they ke chaand 2 tukdon mein taqseem ho gaya, aik tukda pahaad ke peechhey (nazar aata) tha aur doosra tukda us se aagey (doosri taraf nazar aata) tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : (iske) gawah bin jao."
7073,"Shoba ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne abu Mamar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein chaand taqseem hokar 2 tukdey ho gaya, aik tukdey ko pahaad ne dhanp liya (is pahaad ke peechhey nazar aata tha) aur aik tukda pahaad ke uper tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! to gawah reh."
7074,"Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
7075,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur ibne- Adi donon ne Shoba se, Shoba se ibne- Muaz ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, magar ibne-abi Adi ki hadis mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (iske ( gawah bin jao, gawah bin jao."
7076,Sheban ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ahale-Makka ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mutalba kya ke aap unhein (apni nabwooat ki sachchai ki) koi nishani dikhaaein to aap ne unhein chaand ke 2 tukdey hona dikhaya.
7077,"Mamar ne hamein Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Sheban ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
7078,"Yahya-bin-Saeed, Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Abu-Dawud sab ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : chaand 2 tukdon mein phat gaya aur Abu-Dawud (Tiyalisi) ki hadis mein hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein chaand phat gaya."
7079,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein chaand phat gaya."
7080,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya aur abu-Usama ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se, unhon-ne abu Abdur-Rehman Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : takleef deh baatein sun kar Allah se zyada sabr karne wala koi nahi, iske sath dusron ko Sharik thehraya jata hai aur uski aulad banai jati hai phir bhi wo unhein aafiyat mein rakhta hai aur unhein rizq ata karta hai."
7081,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne abu Abdur-Rehman Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, siwaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us qaul ke : aur uski aulad banai jati hai unhon-ne us ( qaul ( ko bayan nahi kya."
7082,"Ubaidullah bin Saeed ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne abu Abdur-Rehman Salma se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Qais ( abu-Musa Ash-ari ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi nahi jo takleef deh baton par jinhein wo sunta hai Allah Taala se zyada sabr karne wala ho, log ( dusron ko) iska Sharik thehratey hain, uski aulad banatey hain aur wo us (sab kuchh (ke bawajud unhein rizq deta hai, aafiyat bakhshta hai aur (jo maangtey hain) ata karta hai."
7083,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Imran jooni se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah tabarak w taala us shakhs se, jisey ahale-jahannam mein sabse kam azab hoga, farmaeyga : agar poori duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai. tumharey paas ho to (azab se chhoot janey ke liye) usey bataur fidya de doge? wo kahega : haan, to wo (Allah taalaa) farmaeyga : maine tum se us waqt jab tum Adam (Alaihissalam) ki pusht mein they, uski nisbat bahut kam ka mutalba kya tha ke tum shirk na karna. mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (aagey ye) farmaya, padhi. aur main tumhen aag mein nahi daalunga, magar tum ne shirk ( karne) ke siwa har cheez se inkar kar diya."
7084,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Imran se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, usi ki tarah, siwaey ( Allah Taala ke) us qaul ke : aur main tumhen aag mein nahi daalunga unhon-ne usey bayan nahi kya."
7085,"Hisham (Dustwaai) ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din kaafir se kaha jaeyga : tumhara kya khayal hai, agar tumharey paas zamin (ki miqdar) bhar sona maujood ho to kya tum (jahannam ke azab se bchney ke liye) usko bataur fidya de doge? wo kahega : haan, to us se kaha jaeyga : tum se to us se bahut aasan mutalba kya gaya tha."
7086,"Saeed bin abi aruba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne (is tarah) kaha : to usse kaha jaeyga : tum jhoot boltey ho, tum se to us se bahut aasan (baat ka ( mutalba kya gaya tha."
7087,"Sheban ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! qiyamat ke roz kaafir ko kis tarah munh ke bal maidaane-hashr mein laya jaeyga ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya jisne usko duniya mein paon ke bal chalaaya hai wo is baat par qaadir nahi ke qiyamat ke din usey munh ke bal chalaaey? Qatada ne ( hadis sunaney ke baad) kaha : kyon nahi, hamarey rab ki izzat ki qism ! (wo qaadir hai)"
7088,"saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din ahale-dozakh mein se us shakhs ko laya jaeyga jo duniya mein sabse zyada aasooda tar aur khush'haal tha, to usey dozakh mein aik baar ghotaa diya jaeyga, phir us se puchha jaeyga ke aey Adam ke betey ! kya tu ney duniya mein kabhi aaraam dekha tha? kya tujh par kabhi chain bhi guzra tha? wo kahega ke Allah ki qism ! aey mere rab ! kabhi nahi aur ahle-jannat mein se aik aisa shakhs laya jaeyga jo duniya mein sab logon se sakht tar takleef mein raha tha. jannat mein aik baar ghotaa diya jaeyga, phir us se puchha jaeyga ke aey Adam ke betey ! to ne kabhi takleef bhi dekhi hai? kya tujh par shiddat aur ranj bhi guzra tha? wo kahega ke Allah ki qism ! mujh par to kabhi takleef nahi guzri aur maine to kabhi shiddat aur sakhti nahi dekhi."
7089,"Hammam-bin-Yahya ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala kisi momin ke sath aik neki ke mamley mein bhi zulm nahi farmata. iske badley usey duniya mein bhi ata karta hai aur aakhirat mein bhi uski jazaa di jati hai. raha kaafir, usey nekiyon ke badley mein jo usney duniya mein Allah ke liye ki hoti hain, usi duniya mein khila (pilaa) diya jata hai yahan tak ke jab wo aakhirat mein pahunchtaa hai to uske paas koi neki baqi nahi hoti jiski usey jazaa di jaey."
7090,"Moatamir ke walid (Sulaiman) ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki : bila shubah aik kaafir jab koi nek kaam karta hai. to uske badley usey duniya ke khaanon ( ne'maton ( mein se aik luqma ( nemat ki sura mein) khila deta hai. aur momin, Allah Taala uski nekiyon ka zakheera aakhirat mein karta jata hai. aur uski itaat shiaarii par duniya main ( bhi) usey rizq ata farmata hai."
7091,"Saeed (bin-abi-Aruba) ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un donon (Hammam aur Sulaiman) ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
7092,"Abdul-Aala ne hamein Mamar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin ki misal kheti ki tarah hai. hawa musalsal usko (eik ya dusri taraf ( jhukaati rehti hai aur momin par musalsal museebatein aati rehti hain. aur munafiq ki misal dewdaar darakht ki tarah hai (jiska tanaa hawa mein bhi tan kar khada rehta hai). hiltaa nahi yahan tak ke (eik hi baar) usey kaat kar gira diya jata hai."
7093,Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath khabar di magar Abdur-Razzaq ki hadis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman : usey jhukaati rehti hai ke bajaey usey modti rehti hai ke alfaz hain.
7094,"Zakariyaa-bin-abi Zayda ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey ne apne walid Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin ki misal kheti ke baareek tili jaisey taney ki hai. hawaa usey mod deti , aik martaba zamin par lita deti hai aur dusri martaba usey seedha karti hai, yahan tak ke wo peelaa ho kar khushk ho jata hai aur kaafir ki misal dewdaar darakht ki si hai jo apni jadon par tan kar khada hota hai, usey koi cheez mod nahi sakti , yahan tak ke iska ukhad kar girnaa aik hi baar hota hai."
7095,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Bishr-bin-sari aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Kab-bin-Malik se, unhon-ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin ki misal kheti ke teli numaa narm taney ki si hai jis ko hwaa modtii rehti hai, kabhi usko lita deti hai aur kabhi khada kar deti hai, yahan tak ke us (ke paak kar katney (ka waqt aa jata hai, aur munafiq ki misal dewdaar ke mazbut jadon waley darakht ki tarah hai, is par (aisi) koi mushkil nahi aati , yahan tak ke aik hi baar wo jadon se ukhad (kar gir) jata hai."
7096,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur Mehmood-bin-ghailaan ne mujhey yahi hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Bishr-bin-sari ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Kab-bin-Malik se, unhon-ne apne walid se, aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, magar Mehmood ne Bishr se apni riwayat mein kaha : kaafir ki misal dewdaar ke darakht ki tarah hai. aur ibne-Hatim ne munafiq ki misal kaha, jis tarah Zuhair ne kaha hai."
7097,"Muhammad-bin-Bashar aur Abdullah-bin-Hashim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Yahya qattaan ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki. ibne-Hashim ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki aur ibne-Bashar ne kaha : ibne-Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne apne walid se. unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, jaisey un sab ki hadis hai. aur un donon ne apni hadis mein kaha : Yahya se riwayat hai : aur kaafir ki misal dewdaar ke darakht jaisi hai."
7098,Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne kaha ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : darakhton mein se aik darakht hai jiske patey nahi jhadtey aur wo darakht musalman ki tarah hai. lihaza mujhey bataao ke wo kon sa darakht hai? to logon ka dhyaan jangal ke mukhtalif darakhton ki taraf gaya. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere dil mein ye khayal aaya ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai. lekin main jhijhak gaya phir wo (log) kehney lagey : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap bataiye ke wo kon sa ( darakht ( hai? kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo khajoor ka darakht hai. ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to maine ye ( baat apne walid (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko batai to unhon-ne kaha : agar tum ne keh diya hota ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai to mere nazdeek ye ( jawab ( falan-falan ( surkh oonton ( se bhi zyada pasandida hota.
7099,"abu-Khaleel zabai ne Mujahid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba se farmaya : mujhey us darakht ke barey mein bataao jiski misal momin jaisi hai. to log jangalon ke darakhton mein se koi ( na koi ( darakht bataaney lagey. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur mere dil mein ya (kaha : ( mere zahan mein ye baat dali gaee ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai main irada karne laga ke bata dun, lekin) wahan ( qaum ke badey log maujood they, to main unki haibat se mutassir ho kar bolney se ruk gaya. jab wo sab khamosh ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo khajoor ka darakht hai."
7100,"ibne-abi najeeh ne Mujahid se riwayat ki, kaha : main Madina tak Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath raha, maine unhein aik hadis ke siwa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi hadis bayan kartey huey nahi suna. unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas they, to aap ke paas khajoor ke taney ka naram goodaa laya gaya. phir un donon (abu-Khaleel Zubai aur Abdullah-bin-Dinar ( ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7101,"saif ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Mujahid ko suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khajoor ke taney ka narm goodaa laya gaya, phir unki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7102,"Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they, aap ne farmaya : mujhey us darakht ke mutaalliq bataao jo aik musalman aadmi se mushabeh (similar) ya ( farmaya : ( ki tarah hai, uske pattey nahi jhadtey. (Imam Muslim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ke shagird ( Ibrahim (bin-Sufiyan) ne kaha : ghaaliban (hamarey shekh) Imam Muslim ne aur wo ( darakht ( apna phal deta hai kaha hoga (lekin mere paas nahi deta likha hai) aur maine apne doosrey sathiyon ke yahan bhi (unke nuskhon mein) yahi paya hai : aur wo har waqt apna phal nahi deta. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to mere dil mein aaya ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai. magar maine Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo nahi bol rahe they, to maine ye baat na-pasand ki ke main boloon aur kuchh kahun. chunanche ( meri baat sun kar) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar tum ye baat keh detey to mujhey ye falan-falan ( surkh oonton ( se zyada pasand hota."
7103,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : shaitan is baat se naa-ummeed ho gaya hai ke jazeera Arab mein Namaz padhney waley uski ibadat karengey lekin wo unke darmyan ladai jhagdey karaaney se (maayoos nahi hua)."
7104,Wakee aur abu-Muawiya donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
7105,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : iblees ka takht samandar par hai. wo apne lashkar rawaana karta rehta hai taake wo fitney barpa karein. uske nazdeek ( shaitnat ke) darjey mein sabse bada wo hai jo zyada bada fitna barpa kare."
7106,"abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu-Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iblees apna takht pani par bichhaata hai. phir wo apne lashkar rawaana karta hai uske sabse zyada qareeb wo hota hai jo sabse bada fitna daalta hai unmein se aik aa kar kehta hai maine falan-falan kaam kya hai. wo kehta hai tum ne kuchh nahi kiya, phir unmein se aik aa kar kehta hai : maine us shakhs ko) jiske sath mein tha) us waqt tak nahi chhoda , yahan tak ke iske aur uski biwi ke darmyan tafreeq (judaai) kara di kaha : wo usko apne qareeb karta hai aur kehta hai tum sabse behtar ho. Aamash ne kaha mera khayal hai us ( abu-Sufiyan Talha-bin-Naafe) ne kaha : phir wo usey apne sath laga leta hai."
7107,abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : shaitan apne lashkaron ko bhejta hai aur wo logon ko fitnon mein daltey hain. uske nazdeek unmein se badey martabey wala wo hota hai jo zyada bada fitna daalta hai.
7108,"Usman-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs bhi nahi magar Allah ne uske sath jinnon mein se uska aik sathi muqarrar kar diya hai (jo usey burai ki taraf maail karta rehta hai.) unhon (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap ke sath bhi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur mere sath bhi lekin Allah Taala ne uske muqaabley mein meri madad farmai hai aur wo musalman ho gaya. isliye (ab) wo mujhey khair ke siwa koi baat nahi kehta."
7109,"Sufiyan aur Ammar bin Ruzaiq donon ne Mansoor se Jarir ki sanad ke sath unhi ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, magar Sufiyan ki hadis mein hai : har shakhs ke liye aik sathi jinon mein se aur aik sathi farishton mein se muqarrar kar diya hai. (jin usey burai ki taraf maail karta hai aur farishta neki ki taraf. faisla khud usi ko karna hota hai.)"
7110,"Urwa ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik raat unke paas se uth kar bahar nikal gaey. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : mujhey aap ke mamley mein shadeed ghairat mehsus hui, phir aap wapas aaey aur dekha ke main kya kar rahi hun (shadeed ghussey ke aalim mein hun) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha! tumhen kya hua hai kya tum ghairat mein mubtala ho gaee ho? maine kaha : mujhey kya hua hai ke mujh jaisi aurat ko (jiski kai saukanein hun) aap jaisey mard par (jo aik ko aik se badh kar mahboob ho) ghairat na aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumharey paas tumhara shaitan aaya tha (aur us ne tumhen shak mein mubtala kiya? ( ) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya mere sath shaitan bhi hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. maine kaha : har insan ke sath shaitan hota hai? aap ne farmaya : haan. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap ke sath bhi hai? aap ne farmaya : haan lekin mere rab ne is par (qaabu paaney mein) meri madad farmai aur wo Islam ley aaya hai."
7111,"Leis ne Bukair se unhon-ne basar-bin Saeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ko mahz iska amal nijat nahi dilaaey ga . aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi? aap ne farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke Allah Taala apni taraf se mujhey apni rehmat se chipa ley, lekin tum seedhey rastey par chalo."
7112,Amr-bin-Haris ne Bukair-bin-Ashajj se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki magar (is mein) kaha : apni rehmat aur Fazal se aur unhon-ne : aur lekin tum seedhey rastey par chalo. bayan nahi kya.
7113,Ayub ne Muhammad (bin Sirin) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ko uska amal jannat mein nahi ley jaeyga puchha gaya : Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke mera rab mujhey apni rehmat mein chipa ley.
7114,"Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad (bin Sirin) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ko iska amal nijat nahi dilaaeyga. sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne arz ki, Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke Allah Taala mujhey apni rehmat aur maghfirat mein chipa ley. aur Ibne-Aun ne is tarah apne hath se bataya aur apne sar ki taraf (rehmat se dhanp leney ka ( ishara kya (farmaya (aur mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke Allah mujhey (is tarah) apni rehmat aur maghfirat se dhanp ley."
7115,"Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi ko uska amal nijat nahi dilaaeyga. unhon ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke Allah Taala mujhey apni rehmat mein le-le."
7116,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Ubaid ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ko iska amal jannat mein nahi ley jaeyga unhon ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne arz ki, Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi? aap ne farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke Allah Taala mujhey apne Fazal aur rehmat se dhanp ley."
7117,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (amal ke aalaa tareen meyaar ke) qareeb tar rehney ki koshish karo. sahi rasta ikhtiyar karo aur yaqin rakho ke tum mein se kisi shakhs ko iska amal nijat nahi dega. unhon-ne (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne arz ki, Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi magar ye ke Allah Taala mujhey apni rehmat aur Fazal se dhanp ley."
7118,"ibne-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
7119,Jarir ne Aamash se guzishta donon sanadon ke sath ibne-Numair ki riwayat ki tarah bayan kya.
7120,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur is mein mazeed kaha : aur khush khabri lo. (ke uski rehmat bahut wasee hai, achchhey amal qabool ho jaaengey.)"
7121,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : tum mein se kisi shakhs ko uska amal na jannat mein ley jaeyga na dozakh se mehfooz rakhega aur na mujhey siwaey Allah ki taraf se rehmat ke (jo nijat ka sabab baneygi.)"
7122,"abdul-Azeez-bin Muhammad aur Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Musa-bin-Aqba ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, wo kaha karti thin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sahi amal karo (aalaa tareen meyaar ke) qareeb tar raho aur (Allah ki rehmat ki) khush-khabri (ki ummeed) rakho. haqiqat yahi hai ke kisi ko uska amal hargiz jannat mein dakhil nahi karega. sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aapko bhi nahi ? farmaya : mujhey bhi nahi siwaey iske ke Allah mujhey apni rehmat se dhanp ley aur jaan rakho ke Allah ke nazdeek mahboob tareen amal wo hai jo hamesha kya jaey chahey kam ho."
7123,Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muttalib ne hamein Musa-bin-Aqba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur khush-khabri (ki ummeed) rakho zikr nahi kya.
7124,"abu-Awana ne Ziyad-bin-Ilaqa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne itni (itni lambi) namazein padhein ke aap ke qadam Mubarak sooj gaey. aap se kaha gaya ke aap is qadr takleef uthatey hain? halanke Allah Taala ne aap ke agley aur pichhley gunahon ki maghfirat farma di hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main Allah Taala ka shukr-guzar banda na banun?"
7125,"Sufiyan ne hamein Ziyad bin Ilaqa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne itna (itna lamba) qiyam kya ke aap ke qadam Mubarak sooj gaey. unhon (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : Allah Taala ne aap ke agley pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye hain (phir is qadr mashaqqat kyon?) to aap ne farmaya : kya main Allah ka shukr-guzar banda na banoon?"
7126,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz padhtey to ( bahut lamba) qiyam kartey yahan tak ke aap ke qadam Mubarak sooj jatey, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap aisa kartey hain. halanke aap ke agley pichhley tamam gunahon ki maghfirat ki (yaqeen dahaani karaai) ja chuki hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Aaisha! kya main (Allah taala ka ( shukr-guzar banda na banun?"
7127,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se aur unhon-ne Shaqiq se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke intizar mein unke ghar ke darwazey par baithey huey they ke itney mein Yazeed bin Muawiya Nakhai hamarey paas se guzrey to ham ne kaha : un ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ko hamarey aaney ki itlaa kar dein wo unke paas gaey to thodi hi der mein Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) aagey aur farmaya : mujhey tumharey aaney ki itlaa kar di gaee thi aur mujhey tumharey paas aaney se sirf ye na-pasandidgi rukawat thi ke main tumhari uktaahat ka sabab na bin jaun. bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi hamarey ukta janey ke dar se sirf kuchh dinon main hi waz w nasihat se nawaaza kartey they."
7128,"abu-Saeed ashajj ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Idrees ne hadis bayan ki, neez hamein Minjaab-bin-Haaris tamimi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Mus-hir ne khabar di, neez hamein Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Ali-bin-khashram ne hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di, neez hamein ibne-abi-Umar ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki, un sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki. aur Minjaab ne apni riwayat mein mazeed ye kaha : ibne-Mus-hir se riwayat hai Aamash ne kaha : aur mujhey Amr-bin-Murra ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
7129,"Mansoor ne Shaqiq abu-Waail se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) hamein har jumerat ke din waz (nasihat) w nasihat farmaya kartey they, to aik shakhs ne kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman! hamein aap ki baatein (bahut) pasand hain aur ham unki taraf shadeed raghbat rakhtey hain. ham chahtey hain ke aap har roz hamein hadisein bayan farmaya karein. unhon-ne kaha : mujhey iske ilawa tumhen hadisein bayan karne se sirf ye na-pasandidgi rukawat hai ke main tumhen uktaahat ka shikar na kar dun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is baat ko na-pasand kartey huey ke ham par uktaahat taari ho jaey kuchh ( khas ( dinon main hi hamein waz (nasihat) w nasihat se nawaza kartey they."
